<paragraph id="99197B6BE9DCE0736AECC91B714764E0" pageId="7" pageNumber="18">
Mazandaran Province, Nowshahr city, pond near Caspian Sea, 
<geoCoordinate id="BF45F2B8BC8070F64EB975B38ABB0FA9" degrees="51" direction="east" minutes="31" orientation="longitude" precision="925" value="51.516666">51°31'E</geoCoordinate>
